  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add onion, ginger, and garlic; sauté until onion is caramelized.",
    "Add cumin powder, coriander powder, turmeric powder, and red chili powder; sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add shrimp; cook until pink, about 2-3 minutes per side.",
    "Add Basmati rice; stir to coat with spices and oil.",
    "Add 2 cups water; bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low; cover and simmer for 18-20 minutes.",
    "Fluff with a fork; garnish with cilantro and black pepper.",
    "Serve hot."
